&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone who:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has completed or is about to complete an Agribusiness/Ag Science degree with a broadacre focus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has a strong affinity with the land&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Is interested in developing an agronomic specialisation&lt;/li&gt;
