&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work in various agricultural roles to expand your knowledge&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scout for potential pests and diseases within crops&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in field trial work for hands-on experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in preparing for client visits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure accurate data recording in our systems&lt;/li&gt;
